## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** generate lighting content (DMX values come from effects)
- ❌ Does **not** handle video playback (use VideoEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** do audio mixing (use AudioEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** provide visual effects (use EffectEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** store show history (use separate logging)
- ❌ Does **not** manage user permissions (use Auth system)

