## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Timeline drift over long shows | Medium | High | High-precision timers, periodic resync |
| Cue timing jitter | Medium | High | Lock-free data structures, real-time scheduling |
| Timecode dropouts | Medium | Medium | Buffer timecode, predictive interpolation |
| Large show file memory usage | Low | Medium | Lazy loading, streaming from disk |
| Multi-user conflicts | Medium | Medium | Operational transform or CRDTs |

